description: Once you try any a bite of any breakfast items or fresh hot fried chicken options from Free Range LA, you too will find their food to be freakishly delish. The Free Range truck is hitting up different coffee spots throughout the week and you’re sure to see them at Melrose Place Farmer’s Market on the weekends, pleasing everyone with their tasty comfort cuisine, including their...Famous Avocado Toast- thick cut sourdough topped with over-easy egg, Hass avocado mash, sriracha drizzle, and pickled onionsThe Original Free Range LA Chicken Sandwich- Tempura-fried free range chicken, fresno chili cole slaw, whole grain honey mustard sauce on a toasted portuguese bun Twice Cooked & Hand-Torn Crispy Potatoes- roasted and fried Russet potatoes with everythings seasoning...and there’s frankly so much more...So for a fun, friendly, and wonderfully scrumptious foodie exchange, come on out to Free Range LA!
name: Free Range LA
